  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Screen reader support:</strong> Some screen readers announce marked text, though support varies</li>
      <li><strong>Color alone:</strong> Don't rely solely on highlight color to convey meaning - add text labels for variants</li>
      <li><strong>High contrast:</strong> Ensure sufficient contrast between highlighted text and background</li>
      <li><strong>Context:</strong> Provide context for why text is highlighted (e.g., "Search results for...")</li>
    </ul>

